Package: projectTPE
Title: A Shiny Application for Latent Factor Analysis of Non-Formal Teacher Performance
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("First", "Last",
           email = "email@institution.ac.id",
           role  = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0000-0000-0000"))
Description: Provides an integrated Shiny-based platform for longitudinal
    latent factor analysis of teacher performance evaluation data in
    composite-score format. Designed for the Indonesian National Assessment
    (Asesmen Nasional) Rapor Pendidikan for non-formal equivalency schools
    (Paket C and PPS Ulya), the application supports exploratory factor
    analysis (EFA), confirmatory factor analysis (CFA) with robust
    estimation, longitudinal measurement invariance testing, and latent
    profile analysis (LPA) — all within a single interactive interface
    requiring no programming expertise. A built-in simulated dataset
    replicates the four-wave (2022-2025) Rapor Pendidikan structure.
